[1] India

[A] Mumbai outbreak: 584 suspected cases since September 2022
Date: Mon 14 Nov 2022
From: Dr. T Jacob John <tjacobjohn@yahoo.co.in> [edited]


Starting in September [2022] there has been a measles outbreak in Mumbai, as reported in The Times of India on 12 Nov 2022 [https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/city/mumbai/over-500-kids-with-suspected-measles-expert-team-in-mumbai/articleshow/95461536.cms].

Of 584 clinically suspected measles reported to the surveillance system, 109 were lab confirmed. A vaccination campaign has been started.

--
